"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"A woman has been awarded $6 million in a verdict that could affect many other cases in the US.\",            \"english_title\": \"Woman Wins $6 Million\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una mujer gan\u00f3 $6 millones en un juicio que puede afectar muchos otros casos en Estados Unidos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Mujer Gana $6 Millones\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The president says if Iran admits to talks, they will be in danger from their own people. Meanwhile, attacks on Iran and Lebanon continue, and two people died from debris in Abu Dhabi.\",            \"english_title\": \"President Warns Iran\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente dice que si Ir\u00e1n acepta hablar, estar\u00e1n en peligro por su propia gente. Mientras tanto, los ataques a Ir\u00e1n y L\u00edbano contin\u00faan, y dos personas murieron por escombros en Abu Dhabi.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente Advierte a Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"There is indirect contact and channels between the two sides, but a deal may still be far away.\",            \"english_title\": \"Indirect Contact\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hay contacto indirecto y canales entre los dos lados, pero un acuerdo puede estar lejos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Contacto Indirecto\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Gulf's hub airports made long-distance travel cheaper, but now their future is uncertain.\",            \"english_title\": \"Gulf Airports Uncertain Future\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los aeropuertos del Golfo hicieron los viajes largos m\u00e1s baratos, pero ahora su futuro es incierto.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Futuro Incierto de Aeropuertos del Golfo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The party, which has been in power since 2019, got the most votes but 